<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8307233>
    dc:description "FIGURE 29. Pauridia serrata subsp. serrata. A, whole plant; B, leaf in transverse section; C, scape apex, bracts and pedicel; D, stamen in dorsal view; E, style and stigma branches; F, ovary in transverse section; G, capsule; H, seed. Scale bar A = 20 mm; B = 1.2 mm; C–E, G = 4 mm; F = 2 mm. Scale bar H = 1 mm. Drawn by Tracey Nowell from Snijman 2380 (NBG!)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8307233/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

